<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Comenzá a Vender | Expertos en Tiendas Online</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #00f2fe;
            --secondary: #4facfe;
            --bg-dark: #0a0e17;
            --card-bg: #161e2d;
            --text-light: #ffffff;
            --text-gray: #a0aec0;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            color: var(--text-light);
            overflow-x: hidden;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* --- NAVEGACIÓN --- */
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 25px 8%;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: 0.4s ease;
        }

        .nav-left i {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px var(--primary));
        }

        .nav-links {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-gray);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* Marca arriba a la derecha */
        .brand-name {
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            padding: 0 15px;
            border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        }

        .btn-nav {
            border: 1px solid var(--primary);
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            background: rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.05);
            color: var(--primary) !important;
        }

        .btn-nav:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: #000 !important;
        }

        /* --- HERO SECTION --- */
        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, #1e3a8a33, #0a0e17);
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero h1 span {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .hero p {
            color: var(--text-gray);
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--secondary), var(--primary));
            color: #000;
            padding: 18px 35px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            transition: 0.3s transform;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.3);
        }

        /* --- SERVICIOS --- */
        .services {
            padding: 100px 8%;
            background-color: #0d131f;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 50px 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            transition: 0.4s;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--primary);
            background: #1c2638;
        }

        .card i {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .card p {
            color: var(--text-gray);
        }

        /* --- FOOTER --- */
        footer {
            padding: 50px 8%;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            color: var(--text-gray);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* --- ANIMACIONES --- */
        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition: all 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .reveal.active {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        /* Mobile */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-links { display: none; } /* En una web real aquí iría un menú hamburguesa */
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav id="navbar">
        <div class="nav-left">
            <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
        </div>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#inicio">Inicio</a></li>
            <li><a href="#servicios">Servicios</a></li>
            <li class="brand-name">Comenzá a Vender</li>
            <li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/comenza_a_vender?igsh=MXhyM20wZzRzZHBzNw==" class="btn-nav" target="_blank">Contacto</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <header id="inicio" class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1 class="reveal">Tu negocio merece una <br><span>Tienda Profesional</span></h1>
            <p class="reveal">Creamos sitios web optimizados para convertir visitantes en clientes. No pierdas más ventas por no estar en internet.</p>
            <div class="cta-group reveal">
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/comenza_a_vender?igsh=MXhyM20wZzRzZHBzNw==" class="btn-primary" target="_blank">
                    <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i> Consultar por Instagram
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="servicios" class="services">
        <h2 class="section-title reveal">Nuestros Servicios</h2>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="card reveal">
                <i class="fas fa-store"></i>
                <h3>E-commerce</h3>
                <p>Tiendas autogestionables configuradas para que vendas las 24 horas del día sin interrupciones.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card reveal">
                <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
                <h3>Webs Corporativas</h3>
                <p>Sitios institucionales con diseño de alta gama que transmiten confianza y profesionalismo.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card reveal">
                <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
                <h3>Optimización</h3>
                <p>Estructuras rápidas y livianas preparadas para escalar y aparecer en los primeros puestos.</p>
